{"lemma":"خَطٌّ","slug":"خَطٌّ","root":"خ.ط.ط","root_slug":"خ-ط-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ط-ط","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":13},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10939"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%8C%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to draw a line"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to draw"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to write"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to carve, inscribe"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to outline, mark"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of خَطَّ (ḵaṭṭa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"line","examples":[{"text":"وبالانتقال والفحص تبين تسرب غاز من المواسير الأرضية بخط الغاز الرئيسى المغذى للقرية.","english":"And through the passthrough and the inspection it came to light the leakage of gas from the earth pipes through the main gas supply line of the village."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stroke"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stripe"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ridge"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"handwriting"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"calligraphy"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"script"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate to Nabataean Aramaic 𐢊𐢋𐢋 (“to pull out; to engrave”), Jewish Babylonian Aramaic חֲטַט (ḥăṭaṭ, “to dig out, to hollow out, to excavate”), Classical Syriac ܚܰܛ (ḥaṭṭ, “to dig out; to excavate; to carve”), Akkadian 𒄩𒁕𒂅 (ḫa-ṭa-ṭu /⁠ḫaṭāṭu⁠/, “to dig out; to dredge; to make an incision”)."},"ipa":["/xatˤ.tˤa/","/xatˤtˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10939","headword_ar":"خَطٌّ","root":"xT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A line, streak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stripe;"},{"kind":"text","text":"in, or upon, a thing: (K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTuwTN","text_ar":"خُطُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoTaATN","text_ar":"اَخْطَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) the latter, [a pl. of pauc.,] used by El-'Ajjáj: (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~apN","text_ar":"خُطَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaT~N","text_ar":"خَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as explained above, being] a subst. form [the inf. n.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxaT~u","text_ar":"الخَطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqoTapN","text_ar":"نُقْطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aqoTu","text_ar":"النَّقْطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K: *) you say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Zahori AlHimaAri xuT~ataAni","text_ar":"عَلَى ظَهْرِ الحِمَارِ خُطَّتَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Upon the back of the ass are two lines,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"streaks, differing in colour from the rest of the body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  [In mathematics,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A line."},{"kind":"text","text":"And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaT~u AlAisotiwaA='i","text_ar":"خَطُّ الاِسْتِوَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The equinoctial line."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A slight track,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"path,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"road, in plain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. as above. (K.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A road,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"path:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, K:) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ailozamo *`lika AlxaT~a walaA taZolimo minohu $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"اِلْزَمْ ذٰلِكَ الخَطَّ وَلَا تَظْلِمْ مِنْهُ شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Keep thou to that road,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"path, and do not deviate"},{"kind":"page_break","n":760},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from it at all"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or in this sense the word is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~N","text_ar":"خُطٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A road,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"street, that is a common thoroughfare;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~N","text_ar":"خُطٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IDrd, K.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A streak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stripe, of herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkalaA^u xuTuwTN fiY AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"الكَلَاُ خُطُوطٌ فِى الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The herbage consists of streaks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stripes, upon the ground;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the rain not having watered the country in common. (L, TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Writing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Handwriting. Character;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"particular form of letters."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b6-  See also 1.]"}],"source_refs":["K","S","TA","Th"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}